NPC.OliverGreen: Howdy Mister.
[if {global.PillarPaint} == `Red`]
    NPC.OliverGreen: Ugh, you agreed to paint it red.
[elseif {global.PillarPaint} == `Green`]
    NPC.OliverGreen: Green, green, green! GO green!!!
    [goto end]
[endif]
NPC.OliverGreen: Would you like this pillar to be green?
* Sure 
    [event Event.Paint.Green]
    [set global.PillarPaint `Green`]
    NPC.OliverGreen: Thanks Mister!
* No way
* I'll think about it.
    NPC.OliverGreen: You have 1 microsecond time to decide.